-- Egypt Court Rejects Appeal by Businessman Ahmed Ezz, MENA
-- B y   T a r e k   E l - T a b l a w y
-- 2012-05-09T14:06:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-09/egypt-court-rejects-appeal-by-businessman-ahmed-ezz-mena.html
Egypt’s top appeals court declined an
appeal by businessman Ahmed Ezz against his conviction and
sentencing for irregularities in awarding steel licenses to  Ezz
Steel (ESRS) , the state-run Middle East News Agency reported.  The court refused to schedule an expedited hearing for
Ezz’s appeal, MENA said today. The businessman had been
sentenced to 10 years in prison in September.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tarek El-Tablawy in Cairo at 
 teltablawy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
